data.name: Credits description contOG
data.value:
This app is a reimagination of the field manual "Identification of Central American, Mexican, and Caribbean Woods" by Drs. Rafael Arévalo and Alex Wiedenhoeft.
Arévalo, Rafael; Wiedenhoeft, Alex C. 2022. [Identificación de las Maderas de Centroamérica, México y el Caribe—Identification of Central American, Mexican, and Caribbean Woods.] General Technical Report FPL-GTR-293. Madison, WI: U.S. Department of Agriculture, Forest Service, Forest Products Laboratory. 376 p. ^https://doi.org/10.2737/FPL-GTR-293|
Image credits: Dominique Belcher (2020) Lencer (2007) “Vorlage Karibik/Mittelamerika, Blank Map Caribbean Sea,” ^https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Caribbean_Sea_and_West_Indies.png|
This material is based upon work that is supported by the National Institute of Food and Agriculture, U.S. Department of Agriculture, McIntire Stennis project under accession number 7004014.
This publication is a contribution of the Forest and Wildlife Research Center, Mississippi State University.
